items.title: Meg's, I never believed in love at first sight until I met you. I was the loner at msu orientation and you came up to me asking if you can sit by me and thank sweet baby Jesus I said yes. You than helped me find my way around, and at that point I knew you were something special. I couldn't let something like that go.One thing led to another, and we became roomies üíü on move in day I asked if you mind if I pee with the door open  LOLOLOL that doesn't even phase us anymore üòÇ we are sooooooooo comfortable around each other it blows my mind. Thinking back to these 2 semesters together I have realized that dull moments are not allowed. The easiest way to say this is we just click, we know exactly how to cheer each other up and make laugh until waterworks takeover. One day we tried to write down all of our insiders but there was no hope... WAY TOO MANY. Not only did i fall in love with you, but also your family. I adore coming to the city of the bay with youüòá I think it's safe to say that no friendship gets into half the shenanigans we do together. I am not just saying this bc it's your birthday and I wanna score some points, but thank you thank you thank you for everything you do for me. Your heart cannot get much bigger, and you inspire me beyond words. HAPPY 20th BIRTHDAY MEGAN RENEE üéä love you best friend and btw.. wooooo  a big shoutout  for beating teen pregnancy üòâ you are the bomb and I feel uncomfortable even thinking what this year would be like without you, you make each day better and better. Fate all the way bbüíã
